{
  "id": "nce2-l95",
  "title": "Lesson 95: A Fantasy",
  "audio": "/audio/nce2/95ÔºçA Fantasy.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Why was the Ambassador particularly lucky?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 9.57,
      "endTime": 14.91
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "When the Ambassador of Escalopia returned home for lunch, his wife got a shock.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 14.92,
      "endTime": 23.21
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "He looked pale and his clothes were in a frightful state.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 23.22,
      "endTime": 28.73
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "'What has happened?' she asked.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.74,
      "endTime": 32.76
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'How did your clothes get into such a mess?'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 32.77,
      "endTime": 37.8
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'A fire extinguisher, my dear,' answered the Ambassador drily.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 37.81,
      "endTime": 43.65
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'University students set the Embassy on fire this morning.'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 43.66,
      "endTime": 48.62
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'Good heavens!' exclaimed his wife.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 48.63,
      "endTime": 52.86
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'And where were you at the time?'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 52.87,
      "endTime": 56.6
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'I was in my office as usual,' answered the Ambassador.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 56.61,
      "endTime": 61.44
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'The fire broke out in the basement.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 61.45,
      "endTime": 64.4
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "I went down immediately, of course, and that fool, Horst,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 64.41,
      "endTime": 69.86
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "aimed a fire extinguisher at me.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 69.87,
      "endTime": 72.79
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He thought I was on fire.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 72.8,
      "endTime": 75.66
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "I must definitely get that fellow posted.'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 75.67,
      "endTime": 80.32
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The Ambassador's wife went on asking questions,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80.33,
      "endTime": 84.39
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "when she suddenly noticed a big hole in her husband's hat.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 84.4,
      "endTime": 90.26
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'And how can you explain that?' she asked.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 90.27,
      "endTime": 94.87
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'Oh, that,' said the Ambassador.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 94.88,
      "endTime": 98.55
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'Someone fired a shot through my office window.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 98.56,
      "endTime": 102.58
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Accurate, don't you think?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 102.59,
      "endTime": 104.87
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Fortunately, I wasn't wearing it at the time.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 104.88,
      "endTime": 109.35
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "If I had been, I would not have been able to get home for lunch.'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 109.36,
      "endTime": 114.36
    }
  ]
}